The global shift to #remotework has created both opportunities and challenges for the future of our workforces. Very interesting article here with extremely valuable insights & fact-based trends of this transformation: 
• Remote collaboration is more difficult, but the transition back to in-person work might be just as hard;
• Based on Brainwaves monitoring: Video meetings lead to fatigue;
• Gen Z and millennials are struggling more than older generations to find balance;
• Working from home drives more empathy among colleagues world-wide;
• Employees feel more included when everyone joins meetings remotely;
